{"tid":2495567,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"21年3月份 MPF 強積金表現 (美股 / 大中華 / 港股)","createTime":"2021-04-19T09:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:23:59.000Z","uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05afb610440ea660f9df3c4ca46c822f15793b35","tid":2495567,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSw8YkyRjYzZHPRnga7CcNsavNACHmU4q5sxm79q22EMY?filename=C15aq8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC15aq8J.jpg&h=9b6608fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW4PezE44tMiQDvtdsj7VtECQnzhUrPYzYfNUKGrMhRjC?filename=jfVJL8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfVJL8L.jpg&h=2dbe0828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRs9p7o7yjVRSGGriSFSquSuXA3ZAZDoE5k6gDuZP1tBg?filename=jhZbaAs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhZbaAs.jpg&h=54439bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本月數據大家會見到個數字係非常靚仔，係因為一年前既3 月美股溶斷左4次，陷全剷左一段好短時間就急速反彈，直到今日為止，S&amp;P500又再破頂，成份股當中有96.62%的公司股價係高過200天平均線，對上一次高位係去返2020年1月16日有84.35%既公司股價高過200天線，<span class=\"red\">而家宜分段注入，不適合一炮過搞整合供款</span><br />\n<br />\n數據來自投資基金公會每月報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkifa.org.hk/chi/Fund-Performance-MPF.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkifa.org.hk%2Fchi%2FFund-Performance-MPF.aspx&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=00ae6f06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkifa.org.hk/chi/Fund-Performance-MPF.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n基準是什麼?<br />\n請參考呢度<a href=\"https://www.ftserussell.com/products/indices/mpf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftserussell.com%2Fproducts%2Findices%2Fmpf&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=7df79262\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftserussell.com/products/indices/mpf</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 北美指數同美國指數有什麼分別?<br />\n北美指數會多咗大概4-5%加拿大股票落去，傳統上加國股票波動較細 (根據基準而家係4.07%加國股票)<br />\n<br />\n2. 恒指同基準的富時香港指數分別?<br />\n恒指係度恒生指數有限公司既出品，包含55隻股<br />\n恒指支國企業指數亦都係得50隻股<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsi.com.hk/static/uploads/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20201113T000000.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsi.com.hk%2Fstatic%2Fuploads%2Fcontents%2Fzh_hk%2Fnews%2FpressRelease%2F20201113T000000.pdf&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=5a472392\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hsi.com.hk/static/uploads/contents/zh_hk/news/pressRelease/20201113T000000.pdf</a><br />\n而富時香港指數係包含本地公司指數92隻及中國指數成份股236隻，總數共328隻<br />\n<br />\n3. 大中華係買緊咩?<br />\n根據基準指數，大概有55%係中國股票，不足20%係香港本地公司股票，餘下20%幾就係台灣股票<br />\n<br />\n4. 宏利康健護理好唔好? 跑贏定跑輸?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2372938/page/4\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2372938/page/4</a><br />\n#77<br />\n比咗個同類型參考指數同ETF去做個參考對比<br />\n<br />\n5. 低息環境仲放唔放錢落極高管理費的債券基金?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2412596/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2412596/page/1</a><br />\n#10<br />\n真正衰過做定期同儲蓄保<br />\n<br />\n6. 做整合/ 轉會前問一問自己以下問題先<br />\n- 間公司有否被動式/ 偏向參考指數基金選擇<br />\n- 同一隻基金有否分A , B類管理費，較貴管理費的20年後可以跑輸比平果隻10%以上，呢個就係複利既影響<br />\n- 間公司有否管理費回贈/ 折扣等，例如宏利一般基金會按你年資同資產值獲得較平管理費，但要小心有D基金如康健護理係一蚊都冇得平的<br />\n- 間公司過往表現，資料可以參考一下週年報告，睇下佢偏離基標幾多，長遠係跑贏定跑輸<br />\n<br />\nRemarks:<br />\n1. 由2020年3月美股大跌前永明AGENT已經係連登放風話會推出美股系列，結果到目前為止都係冇<br />\n2. 近日有自稱宏利既agent電話coldcall, 無恥到第一句就問你有冇收到宏利強積金報告，想呃你做整合，屌你唔好扮熟扮有寄野比人，拒絕不良agent<br />\n3. 各位搵食的agent, 係你留你地個tg同時，請你講明你係代表緊邊間公司"},{"pid":"d7b6f3b825800e8903857232e8b5e505064d427f","tid":2495567,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"萬全搞乜突然咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3ec12a823fd4263a42cbf9fab2e3c992348a7b","tid":2495567,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"all in美股指數又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726ad6d86777a1cda977d9daa6acbd9c7c26c5b2","tid":2495567,"uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"宏利今年好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcf354a5980bd3963f4249e4cd0113b17be3518","tid":2495567,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b6f3b825800e8903857232e8b5e505064d427f","tid":2495567,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"萬全搞乜突然咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"成長股同中小科技類股份受壓左幾個月了，受市場輪動影響"}]}